Are they very, very stiff and
vary by the book.

13
00:00:40.511 --> 00:00:42.935
And all these things will depend and
it's a good chance for

14
00:00:42.935 --> 00:00:45.062
you as the candidates to get a feel for
the company,

15
00:00:45.062 --> 00:00:48.004
it's a good chance as the interviewer
to get a feel for the candidate.

16
00:00:48.004 --> 00:00:52.341
Are they at ease when they code?

17
00:00:52.341 --> 00:00:52.880
Are they relaxed?

18
00:00:52.880 --> 00:00:58.200
But hopefully, you'll give them the option
of the phone screen to code test.

19
00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:01.285
A lot of times, I prefer the phone screen,
we get right to it.

20
00:01:01.285 --> 00:01:03.767
I don't spend any extra of
my time doing code test.

21
